<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11205</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15956</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>美罗城中央银行看上去非常忙碌。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15957</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20111</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要取钱。” 一个顾客说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20112</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23892</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>银行柜员在电脑上输入了信息，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23893</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26524</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现金抽屉打开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26525</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31581</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！” 柜员说，“抽屉里没钱了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31582</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36010</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>请稍等一会儿！我到保险库里去拿。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36011</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41025</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他走向保险库，开了锁，打开了门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41026</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49315</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>银行柜员大吃一惊，说：“钱都不见了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49316</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55014</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇！” 玛拉说，“土星环太美了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55015</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58787</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西和朋友们在学校的电脑室里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58788</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62777</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们正在做一个科学研究课题。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62778</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66857</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我想在土星环上跑圈。” 杰克说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66858</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69113</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>马拉翻了个白眼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69114</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74860</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“杰克，你不能在土星环上跑圈，它不是固体的，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74861</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80522</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>而是由飘浮在行星周围的冰块和石块组成的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80523</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82946</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔看了过来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82947</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85757</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我正在研究第一次登月，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85758</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88444</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你完全可以在月球上跑，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88445</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91770</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>只不过你需要一套宇航服。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91771</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94131</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西也点了点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94132</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99195</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“而且月球上没什么重力，你可以跳得很高。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99196</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101448</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克站了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101449</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104181</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“地球，我是宇航员杰克。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104182</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106066</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我刚降落在月球上，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106067</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108734</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在要试一下‘月球跳’！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108735</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111172</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克使劲儿跳了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111173</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115198</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西，玛拉和特勒尔都笑了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115199</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117856</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾普卡特老师走了过来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117857</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121040</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“杰克，你选好主题了吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121041</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124584</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克挠了挠头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128991</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我大概会研究外星人吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128992</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132206</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾普卡特老师叹了口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132207</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135583</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“请你选一个严肃点儿的主题。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135584</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138843</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>还有，别再跳了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138844</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142464</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好的，老师。” 杰克又坐下了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142465</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146862</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“罗西，你选了什么主题？” 特勒尔问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146863</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151045</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯，” 罗西说，“我选了水星。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151046</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153797</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不过，它不是很有趣。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153798</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156226</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔想了一会儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156227</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159780</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我有个想法！火箭女孩儿！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159781</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162329</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西强忍着不笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162330</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165224</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她知道特勒尔在开玩笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165225</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167738</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“特勒尔，太有意思了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167739</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173065</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不过，火箭女孩儿有比帮我更重要的事情要做。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173066</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175247</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔摇了摇头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175248</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179428</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不，我是说你应该写‘火箭女孩儿’！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179429</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181998</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她可以在宇宙飞行，对吧？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181999</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186072</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>说不定她的速度跟彗星一样快呢！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186073</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188981</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛拉咯咯地笑了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188982</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191660</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“特勒尔，你太搞笑了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191661</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196575</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这比我那外星人的想法还要蠢。” 杰克说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196576</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200527</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，罗西的手表响了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200528</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205238</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我很快就回来。” 她小声对特勒尔说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205239</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207731</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是布洛姆市长的电话。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207732</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210707</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西从电脑室里走了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210708</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213590</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“布洛姆市长，有什么事吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213591</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218779</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“火箭女孩儿，我需要你的帮助！” 布洛姆市长说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218780</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222713</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“美罗城中央银行的保险库被盗了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222714</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226061</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别担心，市长，” 罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226062</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229166</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我马上就到！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>